title: victorius graves skin
body: I ended season 7 as gold in solo queue and i havent had graves before, and a few days ago i got only graves but i didnt got the skin, when i know i should get it. Am i getting only the champ caz i havent had it before? or its a mistake?

replies.body: The rewards are still in the process of being delivered so the skin itself is likely still on its way if you weren't disqualified. If you haven't seen everything in a couple weeks hit us up in a [**ticket**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new)!
same with me i got the ward, icon, and graves champion but still no skin
